Renée Simonot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ren%C3%A9e_Simonot 0 Renée-Jeanne Simonot (born 10 September 1911) is a retired French centenarian actress. She was married to actor Maurice Dorléac, and is the mother of actresses Catherine Deneuve and Françoise Dorléac, and grandmother of actors Christian Vadim and Chiara Mastroianni.
